he Lost City (2005 film)|The Lost City]]''\n| Fico Fellove\n| Also executive producer/director\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Smokin' Aces]]''\n| Stanley Locke\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2007\n| ''[[The Air I Breathe]]''\n| Fingers\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Ocean's Thirteen]]''\n| Terry Benedict\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2008\n| ''[[New York, I Love You]]''\n| Garry\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Beverly Hills Chihuahua]]''\n| Delgado (voice)\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2009\n| ''[[The Pink Panther 2]]''\n| Inspector Vicenzo Brancaleone\n|\n|-\n| ''[[City Island (film)|City Island]]''\n| Vince Rizzo\n| Also producer\n|-\n| ''[[La Linea (film)|La Linea]]''\n| Javier Salazar\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Across the Line: The Exodus of Charlie Wright|Across the Line]]''\n| Jorge Garza\n|\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[5 Days of War]]''\n| [[Mikheil Saakashvili]]\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2012\n| ''[[Cristiada (film)|For Greater Glory]]''\n| [[Enrique Gorostieta|Enrique Gorostieta Velarde]]\n|\n|-\n| ''[[A Dark Truth]]''\n| Jack Begosian\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2013\n| ''[[Open Road (2012 film)|Open Road]]''\n| Chuck\n|\n|-\n| ''[[At Middleton]]''\n| George Hartman\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2014\n| ''[[Let's Be Cops]]''\n| Detective Brolin\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Kill the Messenger (2014 film)|Kill the Messenger]]''\n| Norwin Meneses\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Rob the Mob]]''\n| Big Al\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Rio 2]]''\n| Eduardo (voice)\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2016\n| ''[[Ghostbusters (2016 film)|Ghostbusters]]''<ref>{{cite news|last=Sullivan|first=Kevin|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/07/06/ghostbusters-andy-garcia-michael-k-williams|title=Ghostbusters adds Andy Garcia and Michael K. Williams to the cast|accessdate=July 6, 2015|publisher=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|date=July 6, 2015}}</ref>\n| Mayor Bradley\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Max Steel (film)|Max Steel]]''\n| [[Miles Dredd|Dr. Miles Edwards]]\n|\n|-\n| ''[[True Memoirs of an International Assassin]]''\n| El Toro\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Passengers (2016 film)|Passengers]]''\n| Admiral Norris\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Geostorm]]''\n| President Andrew Palma\n|\n|-\n| rows