medeo Modigliani]]\n| Also executive producer\n|-\n| ''[[Ocean's Twelve]]''\n| Terry Benedict\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2005\n| ''[[The Lazarus Child]]''\n| Jack Heywood\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Lost City (2005 film)|The Lost City]]''\n| Fico Fellove\n| Also executive producer/director\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Smokin' Aces]]''\n| Stanley Locke\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2007\n| ''[[The Air I Breathe]]''\n| Fingers\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Ocean's Thirteen]]''\n| Terry Benedict\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2008\n| ''[[New York, I Love You]]''\n| Garry\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Beverly Hills Chihuahua]]''\n| Delgado (voice)\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2009\n| ''[[The Pink Panther 2]]''\n| Inspector Vicenzo Brancaleone\n|\n|-\n| ''[[City Island (film)|City Island]]''\n| Vince Rizzo\n| Also producer\n|-\n| ''[[La Linea (film)|La Linea]]''\n| Javier Salazar\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Across the Line: The Exodus of Charlie Wright|Across the Line]]''\n| Jorge Garza\n|\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[5 Days of War]]''\n| [[Mikheil Saakashvili]]\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2012\n| ''[[Cristiada (film)|For Greater Glory]]''\n| [[Enrique Gorostieta|Enrique Gorostieta Velarde]]\n|\n|-\n| ''[[A Dark Truth]]''\n| Jack Begosian\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2013\n| ''[[Open Road (2012 film)|Open Road]]''\n| Chuck\n|\n|-\n| ''[[At Middleton]]''\n| George Hartman\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2014\n| ''[[Let's Be Cops]]''\n| Detective Brolin\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Kill the Messenger (2014 film)|Kill the Messenger]]''\n| Norwin Meneses\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Rob the Mob]]''\n| Big Al\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Rio 2]]''\n| Eduardo (voice)\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2016\n| ''[[Ghostbusters (2016 film)|Ghostbusters]]''<ref>{{cite news|last=Sullivan|first=Kevin|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/07/06/ghostbusters-andy-garcia-michael-k-williams|title=Ghostbusters adds Andy Garcia and Michael K. Williams to the cast|accessdate=July 6, 2015|publisher=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|date=July 6, 2015}}</ref>\n| Mayor Bradley\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Max Steel (film)|Max Steel]]''\n| [[Miles Dredd|Dr. Miles Edwards]]\n|\n|-\n| ''[[True Memoirs of an International Assassin]]''\n| El Toro\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Passengers (2016 film)|Passengers]]''\n| Admiral Norris\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Geostorm]]''\n| President Andrew Palma\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=4|2018\n| ''[[Bent (2018 film)|Bent]]''\n| Jimmy Murtha\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Book Club (film)|Book Club]]''\n| Mitchell\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Mamma Mia! Here We Go Again]]''\n| Fernando Cienfuegos\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Mule (2018 film)|The Mule]]''\n| Laton\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''Against the Clock''<ref name=\"Headlock\">[http://www.polishbrothersandassociates.com/headlock.php Polish brothers: ''Headlock''] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714121826/http://www.polishbrothersandassociates.com/headlock.php |date=July 14, 2014 }}</ref>\n| Gerald Hotchkiss\n|\n|-\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2020\n| ''Ana''\n| Rafa\n| \n|-\n| ''[[What About Love (2020 film)|What About Love]]''\n| Peter Tarlton\n| Post-production\n|-\n| rowspan=2|TBA\n| ''[[Words on Bathroom Walls]]''\n| Father Patrick\n| Post-production\n|-\n| ''[[Big Gold Brick]]''\n| Floyd\n| Post-production\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1978\n| ''[[\u00bfQu\u00e9 Pasa, USA?]]''\n| Pepe (Carmen's Boyfriend)\n| \"Here Comes the Bride\"\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[Archie Bunker's Place]]''\n| Manuel\n| \"Building the Restaurant\"\n|-\n| 1981 & 1984\n| ''[[Hill Street Blues]]''\n| Street Kid<br>Ernesto\n| [[Hill Street Station|\"Hill Street Station\"]] & [[List of Hill Street Blues episodes#Season Four (1983\u20131984)| \"Hair Apparent\"]]\n|-\n| 1983\n| ''[[For Love and Honor]]''\n| Medic\n|  \"For Love and Honor\" (pilot)\n|-\n| rowspan=2|1984\n| ''[[Murder, She Wrote]]''\n| Tough Guy #1\n| [[List of Murder, She Wrote episodes#Season One| \"The Murder of Sherlock Holmes\" (pilot)]]\n|-\n| ''[[Brothers (1984 TV series)|Brothers]]''\n| Jose\n| \"Happy Birthday Me!\"\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''[[Alfred Hitchcock Presents (1985 TV series)|The New Alfred Hitchcock Presents]]''\n| Aleja